!NOTICE:

This level possesses an information hazard dubbed "Nonpentennism" which initiates once one acknowledges the existence of '''Level 959'''. Nonpentennism can begin through viewing any piece of information related to the level such as the level number, the level name, this page, any photograph of it, any documented entrances and exits, and more. Due to the extreme danger that this effect poses, '''Level 959''' and any mentions of it have been redacted from the entire database. For more information, read the page below.

!<div class="onlylight">[[File:Question_mark.png|left|150px|link=]]</div><div class="onlydark">[[File:WhiteQuestion_mark.png|left|150px|link=]]</div>
